lead_paragraph: Jackson Bird has edged out uncapped fast bowler Chadd Sayers for a place in Australia's pace attack for the third and final test against South Africa in Adelaide, captain Steve Smith confirmed on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Bird Is the Word for New-Look Australia in Adelaide
